{"id":"lyr_6buO55Ge5oGp_NDM5MQ_0013","text":"像世事並無不可","structure":{"line_index":13,"char_count":7},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","合理性"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["像","世事","無不可"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,2,2,0,3,9],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zoeng6","sai3","si6","bing6","mou4","bat1","ho2"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"像","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"世事","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"並無不可","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「像世事並無不可」將愛情的發生比作世間萬物，認為是自然而然、理所當然的事情。"},"source":{"title":"愛你這樣傻","artists":["黎瑞恩"],"lyricists":["向雪懷"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4391","prev_line_id":"lyr_6buO55Ge5oGp_NDM5MQ_0012","next_line_id":"lyr_6buO55Ge5oGp_NDM5MQ_0014","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6buO55Ge5oGp_NDM5MQ_0014","text":"若愛你是傻 被愛也是傻","structure":{"line_index":14,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","付出","接受"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["愛","傻","被愛"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,5,2,0,2,4,5,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["joek6","oi3","nei5","si6","so4","bei6","oi3","jaa5","si6","so4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"若愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"是","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"傻","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"被","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"是","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"傻","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「若愛你是傻，被愛也是傻」是一個對稱的結構，表達了在愛情中，付出和接受都是一種「傻」，但這種傻是值得的。"},"source":{"title":"愛你這樣傻","artists":["黎瑞恩"],"lyricists":["向雪懷"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4391","prev_line_id":"lyr_6buO55Ge5oGp_NDM5MQ_0013","next_line_id":"lyr_6buO55Ge5oGp_NDM5MQ_0015","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6buO55Ge5oGp_NDM5MQ_0015","text":"多情何必顧忌","structure":{"line_index":15,"char_count":6},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","勇敢"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["多情","何必","顧忌"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[3,0,0,3,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["do1","cing4","ho4","bit1","gu3","gei6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"多情","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"何必","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"顧忌","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「多情何必顧忌」是一個反問句，鼓勵人們在面對愛情時要勇敢，不必過多顧慮。"},"source":{"title":"愛你這樣傻","artists":["黎瑞恩"],"lyricists":["向雪懷"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_4391","prev_line_id":"lyr_6buO55Ge5oGp_NDM5MQ_0014","next_line_id":"lyr_6buO55Ge5oGp_NDM5MQ_0016","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
